h higher rrt (from 11981.58 to 140744.06) and rrt_max (from 259285.0 to 20057270.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio median change ratio: 2.0, rrt median change ratio: 1.6862\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"High client_error_ratio (35.63) and error_ratio (35.63), indicating potential issues in handling client requests.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio median change ratio: 2.0, error_ratio median change ratio: 2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated client_error_ratio (43.64) and error_ratio (43.64), suggesting problems in processing client requests.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio median change ratio: 2.0, error_ratio median change ratio: 2.0\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}
